title: Mid-Year Population Estimates of the Very Old (including Centenarians): England and Wales
summary: Annual mid-year population estimates for those aged 90 and over by sex and single year of age (90 to 104) and the 105 & over age group, 2002-2014, England and Wales (as a whole).
